WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:02.320
Well, good evening, family.

00:00:02.320 --> 00:00:04.994
Thank you for joining me again today.

00:00:04.994 --> 00:00:06.507
I really appreciate it.

00:00:06.920 --> 00:00:11.383
Let's pray tonight and we're going to seek the Lord, but I'll go over some things.

00:00:11.383 --> 00:00:22.800
I've taken some time and was seeking the Lord, and he visited me today, specifically about the church.

00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:27.886
And the things that he was talking to me about were very stern.

00:00:30.080 --> 00:00:55.760
He gave me 1 Corinthians 5:5 and he talked to me about the ministers of the church around the world and what's about to take place to the ones that will not listen, that have not proclaimed that Jesus Christ is coming and there's no urgency behind the pulpit.

00:00:55.760 --> 00:01:04.479
He talked to me about 1 Corinthians 5:5; he gave me the verse specifically for the church.

00:01:04.479 --> 00:01:21.707
And he talked to me about mega ministers that he's come to them, and they have lots of fame, lots of money, lots of status, and clout—whatever you say—all these people follow them.

00:01:22.827 --> 00:01:38.479
And he said, 'I've come to them and I've told them to preach certain messages and I've told them to tell my people that I'm coming, and they've turned a stiff neck toward me and they keep going the direction that they want to go.

00:01:38.479 --> 00:01:41.119
But I'm out of time.

00:01:41.119 --> 00:01:44.159
I'm out of time, Brandon.

00:01:44.159 --> 00:01:50.708
This dispensation of grace, this era, this season that we've been in is coming to an end.

00:01:50.708 --> 00:01:53.279
The Great Tribulation is right upon us.

00:01:53.279 --> 00:01:59.200
And I desire that no man should perish but all come to repentance.

00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:09.920
And because they have not listened, because they've not obeyed what I've asked them to do, seedtime and harvest is now accelerated.

00:02:09.920 --> 00:02:12.620
And whatsoever a man sows, that will he also reap.

00:02:12.620 --> 00:02:15.690
' He said, 'Brandon, I did not do what's about to happen.

00:02:15.690 --> 00:02:19.280
I took my hand off.

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:24.840
' You can read that scripture in just a second.

00:02:37.200 --> 00:02:43.110
What was I saying?

00:02:44.560 --> 00:02:50.239
Acceleration of seedtime and harvest.

00:02:50.239 --> 00:02:54.720
And because of this, what you're about to see is a great shaking in my church.

00:02:54.720 --> 00:03:03.920
He said 2025 was a year of grace for warnings of what I've spoken and said over and over again.

00:03:03.920 --> 00:03:07.680
This will not catch them unaware.

00:03:07.680 --> 00:03:10.226
This will not catch them with their eyes closed.

00:03:10.226 --> 00:03:13.760
They know; they've been warned.

00:03:13.760 --> 00:03:25.040
And what you're about to see in the church is what I've been talking about, what the Lord has had me say over and over again to a lot of the elders.

00:03:25.040 --> 00:03:29.956
And he said, 'Brandon, I'll use you if you say the hard things, and I'm going to say the hard things.

00:03:29.956 --> 00:03:51.622
' And he said to me, 'A lot of these mega pastors that have multiple campuses and large congregations, I've wanted them to say certain things and warn my people that I'm coming and have an urgency behind the pulpit of my soon return, but they still do not.

00:03:52.926 --> 00:03:55.209
Their head is in the sand.

00:03:55.209 --> 00:03:59.146
Their eyes are closed to what's going on around them.

00:04:00.052 --> 00:04:02.893
It's money-based; it's fame-based.

00:04:02.893 --> 00:04:11.599
It's keeping the status quo because you don't want to lose your congregation if you preach a hard word about the Tribulation or the end times.

00:04:11.599 --> 00:04:13.533
So, you don't warn the people.

00:04:13.533 --> 00:04:15.632
You don't tell them what's coming.

00:04:15.632 --> 00:04:22.880
' So I saw 1 Corinthians 5:5.

00:04:22.880 --> 00:04:27.270
He said, 'I'll hand them over so that they don't burn in hell.

00:04:30.240 --> 00:04:36.730
They'll be shaken on this earth, but they'll be greatly tried in the days ahead.

00:04:36.730 --> 00:04:40.000
And you'll see ministers be greatly tried.

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:50.533
' And he showed me specific ones—and I'll not say their names—but he told me these specific ministers.

00:04:50.533 --> 00:04:57.383
And he said, 'These men that you're seeing, these are the ones that will be at the forefront.

00:04:57.383 --> 00:05:09.600
' But he said, 'Brandon, it's a wake-up call for all my church, not just for the ones that are behind the pulpit, but for the whole church.

00:05:09.600 --> 00:05:12.240
It's a cleaning of the house.

00:05:12.240 --> 00:05:15.885
It's separating the wheat from the tares.

00:05:15.885 --> 00:05:18.440
It's getting the bride ready for what's about to take place.

00:05:18.440 --> 00:05:23.520
' And he said, 'I want you to pray into 2026.

00:05:23.520 --> 00:05:26.240
I want you to intercede into 2026.

00:05:26.240 --> 00:05:30.008
' I have had these visitations.

00:05:30.845 --> 00:05:47.600
I'm telling you, Diana has her phone full of words that he'll download about 2026 and 2027, but finishing this year and what he is requiring of his church and what he wants for us to do to bring in the lost.

00:05:47.600 --> 00:05:49.440
And it was a great shaking inside of me.

00:05:49.440 --> 00:05:50.800
I tell you that much.

00:05:50.800 --> 00:05:51.616
I repented.

00:05:51.616 --> 00:05:57.360
I said, 'My goodness, Lord, am I there?

00:05:57.360 --> 00:06:21.520
' Always realizing that he could use anybody—it's not just about me or Diana or our platform that God has given us—but being co-laborers with Christ, doing this with him and attract to deflect, staying vertical.

00:06:21.520 --> 00:06:27.840
I realize that there's a lot of demon-possessed people that follow me.

00:06:27.840 --> 00:06:33.759
I realize there's a lot of people that would try to be a distraction.

00:06:33.759 --> 00:06:38.720
And the Lord said, 'Brandon, there are a lot of demon-possessed people that need to be free.

00:06:38.720 --> 00:06:43.199
' And I don't say that laughing; it's serious.

00:06:43.199 --> 00:06:48.432
But there's a lot of it that the Lord has warned me about: the distractions and staying on course.

00:06:48.432 --> 00:06:50.399
Staying vertical; don't go horizontal.

00:06:50.399 --> 00:06:54.779
You must stay vertical for what's about to take place.

00:06:54.779 --> 00:07:11.909
And he talked to me about certain key political figures that will not be here very much longer.

00:07:11.919 --> 00:07:26.550
He talked to me about many 9/11s, and he emphasized the word 'many'.

00:07:26.560 --> 00:07:27.108
Small but many, many 9/11s.

00:07:27.108 --> 00:07:29.302
And there were people who said, 'What about Kim?

00:07:29.302 --> 00:07:31.634
' He said, 'There will be no more 9/11s.

00:07:31.634 --> 00:07:33.289
There'll be nothing like that.

00:07:33.289 --> 00:07:34.382
' You know what?

00:07:34.382 --> 00:07:37.813
I can't go by what the Lord told Kim.

00:07:37.813 --> 00:07:40.549
I go by what the Lord told me.

00:07:40.549 --> 00:07:52.114
And just like whenever the prophet went before the king and said, 'You are about to die,' but then he repented and he gave him 15 more years.

00:07:52.114 --> 00:07:59.066
There's things that change in the spirit realm, doors that are open in the spirit realm.

00:07:59.066 --> 00:08:00.546
Do you understand?

00:08:00.546 --> 00:08:15.680
Because of a people that have turned their back on God, that have voted in people that are not godly, that are standing for abominations to the Bible.

00:08:15.680 --> 00:08:20.263
So words are altered and changed just like they were in the Bible.

00:08:20.263 --> 00:08:21.223
Do you understand?

00:08:21.223 --> 00:08:25.773
And the Lord said to me, 'There is a different path.

00:08:29.280 --> 00:08:29.600
There are things that have changed in the spirit realm.

00:08:34.868 --> 00:08:35.256
And there are many 9/11s.

00:08:35.256 --> 00:08:45.600
There are many shakings coming,' and that's whenever he warned me that it will not be all of them all at the same time on the same day.

00:08:45.600 --> 00:08:57.519
Some of them will be, but they'll be back-to-back to create instability and fear so that you don't want to live a normal life, that you second-guess the freedoms that you have.

00:08:57.519 --> 00:09:13.040
And that's why they said it would be a flex even in Hawaii, on Oahu, Hawaii, that there's a group there that would try to have a flex, that they even infiltrated our islands.

00:09:13.040 --> 00:09:26.160
And the Lord said, 'You must pray to always be in the right place at the right time, listening to me, praying and seeking my face on a daily basis.

00:09:26.160 --> 00:09:29.440
' And like I said, I don't come on here to stir up fear.

00:09:29.440 --> 00:09:34.160
I come on here to have an urgency to pray.

00:09:34.160 --> 00:09:36.800
And we saw the eight.

00:09:36.800 --> 00:09:39.817
I said, 'I see the seven, but there's one standing out.

00:09:39.817 --> 00:09:41.279
' He wasn't a Democrat.

00:09:41.279 --> 00:09:42.377
That's what I learned.

00:09:42.377 --> 00:09:48.700
He was an independent and he voted with them.

00:09:50.578 --> 00:09:55.600
We give all the glory to Jesus because we all know that he's the potter and we're the clay.

00:10:09.520 --> 00:10:09.840
And how many people tell you, 'Oh, how awesome!

00:10:19.580 --> 00:10:19.960
You can see, you can hear.

00:10:19.960 --> 00:10:26.096
' But what was the rest of the message the same night?

00:10:38.011 --> 00:10:38.617
It was a warning to the church.

00:10:38.617 --> 00:10:48.000
It was a warning to the people about a major event in Times Square.

00:10:48.000 --> 00:10:52.160
John Lennon's song is about communism.

00:10:52.160 --> 00:10:54.133
Who got voted in?

00:10:54.133 --> 00:10:55.067
Socialism.

00:10:55.067 --> 00:10:58.800
Imagine by John Lennon is a socialist song.

00:10:58.800 --> 00:11:05.698
But look who got voted in.

00:11:05.698 --> 00:11:11.440
Not everything is always black and white when the Lord gives me a message.

00:11:11.440 --> 00:11:14.600
It's a type and shadow.

00:11:20.320 --> 00:11:23.256
The Lord's trying to tell you just to look into it; it's symbolic.

00:11:23.256 --> 00:11:27.120
What he is saying is that there's a flash.

00:11:28.900 --> 00:11:31.200
I saw that man on the stage, but I never told you.

00:11:31.200 --> 00:11:37.291
There are things that I'll never reveal, but I see these things when the flash took place.

00:11:41.727 --> 00:11:44.959
When you see in part, you hear in part, and I try to warn you about the other things.

00:11:44.959 --> 00:11:54.959
I've seen many attacks, lone wolf attacks, a 'Red Dawn' experience.

00:11:54.959 --> 00:11:56.639
Watch Cuba.

00:11:56.639 --> 00:11:58.320
Watch Ukraine.

00:11:58.320 --> 00:12:00.880
The Lord said, 'You heard right.

00:12:17.066 --> 00:12:17.404
It was 15 million.

00:12:17.404 --> 00:12:26.499
' Remember I said there was $15 million that was allocated that we're messing with?

00:12:27.160 --> 00:12:32.880
I was praying and he said it was right: 15 million, not 15 billion.

00:12:32.880 --> 00:12:41.039
15 million is easier to hide when it comes to a trillion-dollar budget.

00:12:41.039 --> 00:12:43.200
15 million is much easier to hide.

00:12:46.000 --> 00:12:48.800
You can mess around with 15 million when you have trillions.

00:12:48.800 --> 00:12:55.691
When you're pushing for a lot of corruption, 15 million is really easy to hide.

00:12:55.691 --> 00:13:06.684
When you're dealing with billions, there's a lot of slush funds that people don't realize where that money goes, but it's for biological weapons.

00:13:06.684 --> 00:13:07.839
Biological—there's a lot there.

00:13:14.462 --> 00:13:19.587
And remember I told you I saw 24 billion in a strategic account when Biden was in power.

00:13:19.587 --> 00:13:28.399
I saw 24 billion and it was being manipulated and put into secret accounts around the world.

00:13:28.399 --> 00:13:30.452
Do you remember that?

00:13:30.452 --> 00:13:37.235
I said they were using it and they'll use it for funding their campaigns in the future.

00:13:37.235 --> 00:13:41.120
They know a storm is coming.

00:13:41.120 --> 00:13:48.560
Many of them know a storm is coming, and the same thing with all these people getting stuck on Atlas.

00:13:48.560 --> 00:13:55.737
I told you all Atlas will become nothing watching the days ahead.

00:13:55.737 --> 00:13:58.286
It will become nothing.

00:13:58.286 --> 00:14:09.892
I've prayed over this, but there's another thing that will be what Oral Roberts saw looking at Atlas.

00:14:15.430 --> 00:14:20.960
I see Atlas, but as I'm looking at it, I'm looking at this thing and the Lord says, 'This is not what you're looking for.

00:14:20.960 --> 00:14:32.062
' There's something else bigger coming that will shake the world and it will be a sign of my Son's return.

00:14:32.062 --> 00:14:41.611
There will be fearful sights that you will see that will bring you to your knees.

00:14:41.611 --> 00:14:51.177
For man's hearts will fail them for fear, looking after those things that are coming on the earth.

00:14:54.399 --> 00:14:56.071
And that's what we're about to see.

00:14:56.071 --> 00:15:22.959
And he talked to me today more about the five shakings again: there'll be a shaking in politics, there'll be a shaking in the earth's crust, there'll be a shaking in the heavens, there'll be a shaking in the finances, and there'll be a shaking in my church.

00:15:26.320 --> 00:15:33.097
And there'll be shakings to the point where they'll all happen like labor pains upon a woman—back-to-back events happening all the time.

00:15:33.097 --> 00:15:33.760
Finances?

00:15:33.760 --> 00:15:35.182
'The sky is falling.

00:15:35.182 --> 00:15:36.036
' Politics?

00:15:36.036 --> 00:15:40.159
People are saying, 'What's going on?

00:15:40.159 --> 00:15:43.451
' with what we see with the standoff.

00:15:56.959 --> 00:15:57.269
But the Lord said, 'I want you to pray into 2026 and I'll reveal things to you.

00:15:57.269 --> 00:16:00.240
' I started interceding and I saw the budget.

00:16:00.240 --> 00:16:04.320
I've warned you about Trump walking a pig that had makeup on, and it was the housing market.

00:16:04.680 --> 00:16:14.022
And as he was walking the pig and parading the pig, this new idea, the housing market started to go up.

00:16:14.022 --> 00:16:20.560
People were excited about this new pig idea, but a pig's still a pig; it's not good.

00:16:20.560 --> 00:16:27.867
And he comes out after I gave this word with a 50-year mortgage.

00:16:27.867 --> 00:16:29.013
50-year mortgage!

00:16:29.013 --> 00:16:32.560
Oh, what a deal that is; you'll pay on your house for your whole life.

00:16:32.560 --> 00:16:38.800
I'm not trying to criticize because I know he watches, but it's just truth, sir: it's a pig.

00:16:46.301 --> 00:16:46.639
I just have to be bold and tell you the truth; it's a pig.

00:17:03.218 --> 00:17:03.413
And the Lord said the 50-year mortgage is not a good deal for the people.

00:17:03.413 --> 00:17:06.900
You'll pay interest for three times what that house is worth over the 50 years.

00:17:06.900 --> 00:17:22.435
So if you borrow a million dollars on a home, on the average house in California, you're going to pay over $5 million on that house if at 7% interest—or whatever it is—you'll pay over $5 million over 50 years.

00:17:22.435 --> 00:17:23.724
That's a terrible deal.

00:17:40.251 --> 00:17:40.582
But I believe it will pass and people will get this going, and the banks will do this because I saw him walking in the housing market, remember?

00:17:45.890 --> 00:17:46.200
And it was transparent; it wasn't solid.

00:17:46.820 --> 00:17:56.200
And I saw, come January in the next two months, there was some kind of something coming, and he had a golden quill in his hand, and it looked like something like the Declaration of Independence.

00:17:56.200 --> 00:17:59.340
There was something that he's about to sign.

00:18:01.306 --> 00:18:01.510
I saw this timeframe.

00:18:01.510 --> 00:18:03.680
Now, what year is it?

00:18:03.680 --> 00:18:07.616
That's what you have to know.

00:18:07.616 --> 00:18:12.697
When you're seeing in part, hearing in part, you don't always know what year it is, but you know it's coming.

00:18:12.697 --> 00:18:21.211
People wanted to know about the hollyberry bush: 'Brandon, is this the year of the major hollyberry bush, the red when the angel came to you and talked to you?

00:18:21.211 --> 00:18:22.034
' I remember.

00:18:22.738 --> 00:18:23.360
It was a life-exchanging experience with the Lord.

00:18:23.840 --> 00:18:24.320
I remember everything.

00:18:25.590 --> 00:18:29.339
The angel came to me and put his hands on my lips and he said, 'Brandon, you must be still.

00:18:29.339 --> 00:18:30.090
They're not dead yet.

00:18:30.090 --> 00:18:31.680
They can't handle it.

00:18:31.680 --> 00:18:40.253
' I said, 'Well, I want to tell them about the investments which you've given me.

00:18:40.253 --> 00:18:46.754
' And he said, 'They're not dead yet; you must be still.

00:18:46.754 --> 00:18:51.497
' And he said, 'Watch the hollyberry bush,' remember?

00:18:52.629 --> 00:19:00.960
And it was turning red, and the berries are red, and it was about the timeframe that a major crash would take place.

00:19:02.503 --> 00:19:03.006
And I saw the snowfall.

00:19:05.817 --> 00:19:06.034
I saw an Aston Martin in the driveway.

00:19:06.034 --> 00:19:15.280
There were things that the Lord showed me specifically, but I wrote on the copper pot that was tempered—it was all tattered and beat up—and I wrote a name.

00:19:17.410 --> 00:19:19.299
And I can't do that because everyone goes, 'You're trying to write the name!

00:19:23.073 --> 00:19:23.507
I know what you're writing!

00:19:23.507 --> 00:19:31.360
' No, I'm not telling you what it is, because the Lord said 'no' and the angel said, 'Shh.

00:19:31.360 --> 00:19:37.840
' But I'm telling you, I saw in this timeframe, it was during the winter months, I saw a major crash.

00:19:37.840 --> 00:19:41.733
Is it this year?

00:19:41.733 --> 00:19:47.910
No, I don't believe it's this year.

00:19:47.910 --> 00:19:55.712
Do I believe it's because there's a lot of people who think that the economic crisis is coming?

00:19:57.920 --> 00:20:01.726
The Lord said, 'I'm giving you a window.

00:20:01.726 --> 00:20:04.684
' This is my opinion.

00:20:04.684 --> 00:20:17.493
So if we go into a deep depression in January, you can't sit there and say, 'Well, you told us it was going to be great times.

00:20:17.493 --> 00:20:33.778
' That is in my opinion what the Holy Spirit told me, and I come on here and I pray with you and I tell you what I feel like the Lord's telling me.

00:20:33.778 --> 00:20:37.280
If it's wrong, I apologize; I'm human.

00:20:37.280 --> 00:20:50.453
But I tell you by what I feel in my spirit.

00:20:50.453 --> 00:20:58.720
It's me getting a perfect message from an imperfect vessel.

00:20:58.720 --> 00:21:12.000
I'm only perfected by his blood, and it's coming through a pipe that sometimes has stuff in it.

00:21:19.644 --> 00:21:30.380
I might have had a bad day, you know?

00:21:30.980 --> 00:21:32.647
And people say, 'Well, that's not like the people in the Bible.

00:21:32.647 --> 00:21:36.180
' And Brandon, I never claimed to be a prophet; never did.

00:21:36.180 --> 00:21:39.640
People try to label me that all the time.

00:21:39.640 --> 00:21:46.736
Watch me; I tell you, I'm here to pray.

00:21:53.839 --> 00:21:55.120
The Lord said, 'You're called to intercede.

00:22:05.662 --> 00:22:05.840
Pray for the nations, Brandon.

00:22:05.840 --> 00:22:08.869
' And I do.

00:22:08.869 --> 00:22:25.713
And he said, 'I'll show you what's to come and you can pray for it.

00:22:25.713 --> 00:22:29.440
' So I do the best I can.

00:22:29.440 --> 00:22:42.000
I saw that angel coming to me and telling me that.

00:23:11.039 --> 00:23:12.158
He said, 'And then I've warned you about a major shaking of the finances.

00:23:20.000 --> 00:23:26.026
I warned you about all these things, but the Lord said, "I'm giving you a window.

00:23:26.026 --> 00:23:30.080
"' And a wave that's transparent will happen.

00:23:30.827 --> 00:23:35.880
And I saw it come, and it was at the beginning of the year.

00:23:35.880 --> 00:23:42.080
And a wave came and the finances were there.

00:23:42.080 --> 00:23:54.560
And great blessing was on the body of Christ for a window of time.

00:23:54.560 --> 00:23:59.1000
It didn't last very long; the wave didn't last very long.

00:23:59.1000 --> 00:24:04.940
And as the ground was gold—all on the gold was about that much—he said, 'Fill your pockets.

00:24:04.940 --> 00:24:08.710
Fill your pockets.

00:24:08.720 --> 00:24:18.260
For there's not much there, but it's enough to get you in the overflow for what's coming, for a great storm is coming.

00:24:18.260 --> 00:24:31.349
' A great storm is coming, and he still talks about that storm almost every day, warning me, keeping me on track, praying in the spirit.

00:24:39.440 --> 00:24:39.720
So, this is what I have for you today.

00:24:44.045 --> 00:24:44.411
I saw a major political figure in Israel be taken out.

00:24:44.411 --> 00:24:47.227
It will shake the nation.

00:24:49.400 --> 00:24:51.299
I saw old faces coming back because of this man.

00:24:51.299 --> 00:24:52.799
A great shaking is coming.

00:24:59.470 --> 00:24:59.980
The Lord said the third temple will be negotiated soon.

00:24:59.980 --> 00:25:05.262
There will be an acceleration of things in Israel with my people.

00:25:25.157 --> 00:25:26.216
But I can't say that word.

00:25:26.216 --> 00:25:33.840
He said, 'Be still no more.

00:25:33.840 --> 00:25:40.510
' You know, when you're on live and I have to watch what I say.

00:25:42.640 --> 00:25:51.750
The Lord said there will be things that I tell you from now on that you're not going to be able to talk about everything anymore.

00:25:51.760 --> 00:25:58.068
But we must pray now for Black Friday, specifically about the Mall of America and the Atlanta airport.

00:26:02.560 --> 00:26:05.279
